##########################################################

Before installing and running Chooch you need to install
the PGPLOT library of graphical subroutines.

The gzipped tar archive can be downloaded 
from http://astro.caltech.edu/%7Etjp/pgplot/install.html

Detailed installation instructions can be found at the same URL
and documentation for PGPLOT if you think you require it is
at http://astro.caltech.edu/%7Etjp/pgplot.

Enjoy!